StructureDefinition-CareConnect-Contract-1

A formal agreement between parties regarding the conduct of business, exchange of information or other matters.

Profile Minimum Viable Content (MVC)

This FHIR profile has no mandatory elements.

Formal Views of Profile Content

Description of Profiles, Differentials, and Snapshots.

The official URL for this profile is: https://fhir.hl7.org.uk/STU3/StructureDefinition/CareConnect-Contract-1

Published on Mon Mar 04 15:21:35 GMT 2019 as draft by NHS Digital.
